{"tid":1380762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「光復元朗」發起人鍾健平 現今疑遭打傷留院軟禁","createTime":"2019-07-29T05:50:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T06:13:20.000Z","uid":53524,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ae987c47f96c44143954376f423bc9e64c461d49","tid":1380762,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:50:16.000Z","msg":"上周六(27日)「光復元朗」遊行不獲警方批准，事件演變成激烈衝突收場，發起人鍾健平聲稱當天只是一個人行街、購物，並非遊行。警方昨(28日)拘捕鍾，涉嫌「組織未經批准集結」接受調查。警方今(29日)表示，鍾因有受傷被送往大埔那打素醫院接受治療，暫未獲保釋。東網記者到該院視察，發現病房外有兩名警員看守。 <br />\n<br />\n遊行另一申請人巫堃泰回覆東網指，警方昨帶同鍾到勝利道一處及其位於元朗教育路的住所搜查。 <br />\n<br />\n鍾昨日出席一個論壇後被警方拘捕，有指他一度被押返跑馬地警署。巫堃泰指鍾昨晚8時53分被警方從大埔警署帶走，警方聲稱帶鍾回其元朗住所搜查。"},{"pid":"372a07dcdf543934f085b01a1583d08dc1e1ad73","tid":1380762,"uid":132770,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:51:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1AvSkE5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1AvSkE5.jpg&h=597822d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"23d9f1d25050d006e7c9509e323c6b8575993c93","tid":1380762,"uid":25831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:52:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f024da080acc23510939f5140cbf5dff48b15c47","tid":1380762,"uid":11436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:52:38.000Z","msg":"痴撚線黑警幾時死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"271e87e0aa87e9e74d41c84b2a3816d9076eaf32","tid":1380762,"uid":121459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:52:56.000Z","msg":"死黑警"},{"pid":"0cb79b1fae14d782de659d046e16afd14b33a738","tid":1380762,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:54:53.000Z","msg":"今時今日仲玩電話簿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a6217702d5faa7eaf2e36173bae82c472da385f","tid":1380762,"uid":235580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:56:07.000Z","msg":"全部手足同我推！ 如何令